c: 66
v: 3
t: "And when the prophet confided to some (of) his wives an information/speech, so when she informed with it (others) and God made it apparent/visible on (to) him, he made some of it known and he opposed from some, so when he informed her with it, she said: \"Who informed you (of) this?\" He said: \"The knowledgeable, the expert/experienced informed me"